  "title": "5 days Accounts Executive up to $3800 (Clementi)",
  "description": "<p>Accounts Executive</p><p>Working Hours: Monday–Friday, 9:00am–6:30pm</p><p>Salary: SGD 3,200 – 3,800</p><p>Location: Clementi</p><p>Benefits: AWS, Performance Bonus, Annual Leave (12–14 days)</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Handle full set of accounts independently (AP, AR, GL, reconciliations)</li><li>Process daily accounting transactions, payments, and journal entries</li><li>Perform bank, intercompany, and key account reconciliations</li><li>Monitor cash flow and support payment processing</li><li>Prepare GST submissions, sales reports, financial statements, and management reports</li><li>Support ERP system implementation and enhancements</li><li>Liaise with auditors, tax agents, and external parties</li><li>Perform ad-hoc accounting duties as assigned</li></ul><p></p><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Diploma or higher qualification in Accountancy or related discipline</li><li>Minimum 1–2 years of relevant accounting experience</li><li>Proficient in MS Excel and accounting software</li><li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision</li><li>Meticulous, organised, and numerically strong</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Company Name: Talent Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 24C2338</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Loke Sai Lye (Loke)</p><p>EA Personnel No: R24123366</p><p>Email: loke.dexter@talentrecruitmentsg.com</p><p>Contact Number: 8168 8648</p>",
